===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|abyen}}, {{m|enm|abye}},<ref name=RHD>{{R:RHCD|page=7}}</ref> {{m|enm|abien}}, {{m|enm|abiggen}},<ref name=WI3/> from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|abycgan|ābyćġan|to buy, pay for, buy off, requite, recompense, redeem, perform, execute}}, from {{m|ang|ā-}} + {{m|ang|bycgan||to buy}},<ref name=WI3>{{R:MW3 1976|page=8}}</ref> equivalent to {{prefix|a|buy|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{etyl|got|-}} {{m|got|𐌿𐍃𐌱𐌿𐌲𐌾𐌰𐌽|sc=Goth}}.<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=11}}</ref>

